{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/cs/design-pattern/creational/factory-method/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>Factory Method Pattern</h1>\n<h2>팩토리 메서드 패턴이란?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>팩토리 메서드 패턴은 부모(상위)클래스에 알려지지 않은 추상 클래스를 생성하는 패턴으로 자식(하위)클래스가 직접 어떤 객체를 생성할지 결정하도록 하는 패턴!</li>\n<li>즉, 객체 생성을 위한 패턴으로 생성과 사용의 분리를 통해서 유연하게 객체를 생성할 수 있게 된다.</li>\n<li>또한 객체 생성에 필요한 과정들을 템플릿처럼 정해놓고 각 과정을 구현할 수 있다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/f8250/architecture.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.8125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/a59e9/architecture.webp 192w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/0ca9f/architecture.webp 384w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/dc9b9/architecture.webp 768w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/e2c2f/architecture.webp 1152w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/f3efb/architecture.webp 1536w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/c3387/architecture.webp 2872w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/3b721/architecture.png 192w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/66595/architecture.png 384w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/fe486/architecture.png 768w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/d2d74/architecture.png 1152w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/e8464/architecture.png 1536w,\n/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/f8250/architecture.png 2872w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/887c4ea2cbe3617895ac2a5829ae9c08/fe486/architecture.png\"\n            alt=\"image\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>왜 사용하나요?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>생성자 (Creator)와 구현 객체(concrete product)의 강한 결합을 피함</li>\n<li>객체가 생성될때 반복적으로 할 일을 수행시킬 수 있음</li>\n<li>캡슐화, 추상화를 통해 생성되는 객체의 구체적인 타입 은닉</li>\n<li>단일 책임 원칙 (SRP) 준수\n<ul>\n<li>객체 생성 코드를 한 곳 (패키지, 클래스 등)으로 이동시켜 코드를 유지보수하기 쉽게할 수 있으므로 원칙을 만족</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>개방 폐쇄 원칙 (OCP) 준수\n<ul>\n<li>기존 코드를 수정하지 않고 새로운 유형의 제품 인스턴스를 프로그램에 도입할 수 있음 (확정성 증가)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>생성에 대한 인터페이스 부분과 생성에 대한 구현 부분을 따로 나뉘었기 때문에 패키지 분리하여 개별로 여러 개발자가 협업을 통해 개발가능\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/6068e/interface.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.1875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/a59e9/interface.webp 192w,\n/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/0ca9f/interface.webp 384w,\n/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/dc9b9/interface.webp 768w,\n/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/e2c2f/interface.webp 1152w,\n/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/e8733/interface.webp 1508w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/3b721/interface.png 192w,\n/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/66595/interface.png 384w,\n/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/fe486/interface.png 768w,\n/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/d2d74/interface.png 1152w,\n/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/6068e/interface.png 1508w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/2ca7243bb2d69d8bbff6f694d3f4d51a/fe486/interface.png\"\n            alt=\"image\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>언제 사용하나요?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>클래스의 생성과 사용 로직 분리로 결합도를 낮춰야 할때</li>\n<li>캡슐화를 통해 정보 은닉이 필요한 경우</li>\n<li>사용자가 구성요소를 확장할 수 있도록 제공해야 할때(라이브러리, 프레임워크 만들때 유용)</li>\n<li>기존 객체를 재구성하는 대신 기존 객체를 재사용하여 리소스 절약하고자 할 때</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>문제점</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>각 제품 구현체마다 팩토리 객체들을 생성해야하기 때문에, 구현체가 늘어날때 마다 팩토리 클래스가 증가 (서브 클래스 증가)</li>\n<li>코드 복잡성 증가</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>구현 방법 (자바)</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/38095/uml.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.729166666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/a59e9/uml.webp 192w,\n/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/0ca9f/uml.webp 384w,\n/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/dc9b9/uml.webp 768w,\n/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/8c31b/uml.webp 827w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/3b721/uml.png 192w,\n/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/66595/uml.png 384w,\n/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/fe486/uml.png 768w,\n/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/38095/uml.png 827w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/79bba52632168da624a54e858cb9e9cf/fe486/uml.png\"\n            alt=\"UML\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/5onchangwoo/design-pattern/tree/main/src/com/example/dessignpattern/creational/factorymethod\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">자바 코드 보러가기</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"디자인 패턴 - 팩토리 메서드","summary":"디자인 패턴의 생성패턴 중 하나인 팩토리 메서드 패턴에 대해서 알아보기","date":"2023.06.08.","categories":["cs","design-pattern"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/368f999e524384af26a4adc508facc4d/fef98/defalut-thumbnail.png","srcSet":"/static/368f999e524384af26a4adc508facc4d/5d695/defalut-thumbnail.png 150w,\n/static/368f999e524384af26a4adc508facc4d/f3ecd/defalut-thumbnail.png 300w,\n/static/368f999e524384af26a4adc508facc4d/fef98/defalut-thumbnail.png 600w","sizes":"(min-width: 600px) 600px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/368f999e524384af26a4adc508facc4d/0526f/defalut-thumbnail.webp 150w,\n/static/368f999e524384af26a4adc508facc4d/6ab4e/defalut-thumbnail.webp 300w,\n/static/368f999e524384af26a4adc508facc4d/06ea9/defalut-thumbnail.webp 600w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 600px) 600px, 100vw"}]},"width":600,"height":800}},"publicURL":"/static/368f999e524384af26a4adc508facc4d/defalut-thumbnail.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/cs/design-pattern/creational/factory-method/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}